{"type": "article", "id": 17902, "title": "朋友圈也有让人心情舒畅的东西，比如这 23 件小事", "description": "哎呀，说起来生活还是很美好的。", "date": "2015-11-22T07:31:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6475, "name": "朋友圈"}], "category": 5, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 90, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605220154g56FRT87w2LSlIuh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>1. 一直不懂表达某种情绪，突然看到这张表情。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220140n4iDTQZkYbtKAMjI.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 2. </strong></span><strong>猫猫狗狗小视频。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220140GHoufPIsid5O8e0U.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.74698795\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 3.</strong></span><strong>不知道的八卦。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220141OrgMehndmw3ZHi4X.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.10055866\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 4. 能看见</strong></span><strong>“此条我分了组</strong><strong>/</strong><strong>屏蔽了组”。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052201418OmugyscPxwWljGn.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.58232932\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 5. </strong></span><strong>上课，有人偷拍同学睡觉。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220142kSrFu8IV4Nda9wPf.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 6. </strong></span><strong>开会，同事偷拍了老板好傻的表情。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220142E7vCdUxbKok0TFW6.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> <strong>7. 熟人</strong></span><strong>红包群入口（别问我为什么觉得生人红包捡起来不体面）。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220143TYdFobrm2HE7VlIJ.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.3321492\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 8. </strong></span><strong>正在因为没抢到演唱会的票桑心，有人发临时加班需转让。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220143IzhyMBWgLpfoKj80.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 9. </strong></span><strong>正在淘宝找代购很焦虑，有人发要去</strong><strong>XXX</strong><strong>旅游要带东西请私信。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220144pNlJgv5To71f8Vzn.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 10. </strong></span><strong>正在无聊的深渊痛苦，有人提醒《国土资源》最新一季已出。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220145XmQwZ0LzR3OCBINl.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.474\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 11. </strong></span><strong>所有人都在安利一部电影，正好我也喜欢。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052201467hVR0rZd8nwPlk3j.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 12. </strong></span><strong>剧透来的防不胜防，还好我昨天看过了。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052201465KvcWz9TwRaU6QLi.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 13.</strong></span><strong>关于我喜欢的</strong><strong> CP </strong><strong>的一切。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052201477lsc0814Rg93TDeN.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.55494505\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 14.</strong></span><strong>顺着一个有趣的标题，找到一个睡前必看的号。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052201470dKukTNUDqiZSLjO.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.79166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 15.</strong></span><strong>评论吐的一手好槽。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052201484I3OgvdPSRt1aTXi.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 16.</strong></span><strong>回复再次戳中笑点。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144931UVdubxcR6pXnzKCq.gif\" width=\"200\" height=\"151\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.755\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 17.</strong></span><strong>加入，排队。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220148knCjBTNd4tV9UZJ7.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong> </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 18.</strong></span><strong>这个餐馆看起来好好吃地址就在家旁边。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220149bsKmUwrpAPG3MCla.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 19.</strong></span><strong>同事又烤了一箱泡芙，说明天带给同事尝。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220150NQInBVMzLHqmosU8.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66959922\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong> </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 20.</strong></span><strong>说我美，任何形式。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220150ePrOsNDpxIEdfHC7.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 21.</strong></span><strong>表扬我，任何形式。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220152A7STtGzI3obOmwCR.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.91\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 22.</strong></span><strong>不讨厌的人。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220153JEFpyevYjGRDx60Z.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong> 23.</strong></span><strong>给我点赞。无所谓那个人讨不讨厌。</strong><strong> </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220154tmcIGUp9fKE8715r.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.76694915\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><em>好奇心研究所的微博（</em><a href=\"http://weibo.com/p/1006065587974982/home?from=page_100606&amp;mod=TAB#place\" target=\"_blank\"><em>@好奇心研究所</em></a><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em>）和微信公众号（ID：</em></span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em>QLab42</em></span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em>）全面上线啦，微信直接搜索「好奇心研究所」就可以订阅，关注与所长亲密接触，赶紧的。</em></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}